### Test BrewSessions API Endpoints

### Get all brew sessions
GET {{BrewLog.Api_HostAddress}}/api/brewsessions

### Get brew sessions with filters
GET {{BrewLog.Api_HostAddress}}/api/brewsessions?method=0&minRating=7&isFavorite=true

### Get brew sessions filtered by date range
GET {{BrewLog.Api_HostAddress}}/api/brewsessions?createdAfter=2024-01-01T00:00:00Z&createdBefore=2024-12-31T23:59:59Z

### Get brew sessions filtered by coffee bean
GET {{BrewLog.Api_HostAddress}}/api/brewsessions?coffeeBeanId=1

### Get brew sessions filtered by temperature range
GET {{BrewLog.Api_HostAddress}}/api/brewsessions?minWaterTemperature=90&maxWaterTemperature=95

### Get brew sessions filtered by rating range
GET {{BrewLog.Api_HostAddress}}/api/brewsessions?minRating=8&maxRating=10

### Get brew session by ID
GET {{BrewLog.Api_HostAddress}}/api/brewsessions/1

### Create new brew session (Espresso)
POST {{BrewLog.Api_HostAddress}}/api/brewsessions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "method": 0,
  "waterTemperature": 93.5,
  "brewTime": "00:00:25",
  "tastingNotes": "Rich crema, balanced flavor with chocolate notes",
  "rating": 8,
  "isFavorite": false,
  "coffeeBeanId": 1,
  "grindSettingId": 1,
  "brewingEquipmentId": 1
}

