### Update brew session
PUT {{BrewLog.Api_HostAddress}}/api/brewsessions/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "method": 0,
  "waterTemperature": 94.0,
  "brewTime": "00:00:28",
  "tastingNotes": "Updated: Excellent crema, perfect extraction with dark chocolate notes",
  "rating": 9,
  "isFavorite": true,
  "coffeeBeanId": 1,
  "grindSettingId": 1,
  "brewingEquipmentId": 1
}

### Delete brew session
DELETE {{BrewLog.Api_HostAddress}}/api/brewsessions/1

### Toggle favorite status
POST {{BrewLog.Api_HostAddress}}/api/brewsessions/1/favorite

### Get favorite brew sessions
GET {{BrewLog.Api_HostAddress}}/api/brewsessions/favorites

### Get recent brew sessions
GET {{BrewLog.Api_HostAddress}}/api/brewsessions/recent?count=5

### Get top rated brew sessions
GET {{BrewLog.Api_HostAddress}}/api/brewsessions/top-rated?count=10

### Advanced filtering examples

### Get espresso sessions with high ratings
GET {{BrewLog.Api_HostAddress}}/api/brewsessions?method=0&minRating=8

### Get pour over sessions from last month
GET {{BrewLog.Api_HostAddress}}/api/brewsessions?method=2&createdAfter=2024-01-01T00:00:00Z

### Get sessions with specific equipment
GET {{BrewLog.Api_HostAddress}}/api/brewsessions?brewingEquipmentId=1

### Get sessions with specific grind setting
GET {{BrewLog.Api_HostAddress}}/api/brewsessions?grindSettingId=2

### Get only favorite sessions with high ratings
GET {{BrewLog.Api_HostAddress}}/api/brewsessions?isFavorite=true&minRating=9

### Brew Method Reference:
# 0 = Espresso
# 1 = FrenchPress  
# 2 = PourOver
# 3 = Drip
# 4 = AeroPress
# 5 = ColdBrew